<P><H1 align=center>DC260 – ADD/EDIT BUILDER DETAILS</H1>
<P></P>
<P><FONT color=red>Areas in red text are mandatory and must 
be completed.</FONT>         </P>
<P><H3>Company name: </H3>The directory search button will take 
you to a screen that allows you to search for the name of the company you want 
to input. Input the name of the company and click on directory search. Select 
the company when shown and click on ‘select’, this will transfer the details 
already held to the details screen. If the company name is not on the Directory 
search, you will need to type it in the field manually.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Is in the directory: </H3>Click <STRONG>No </STRONG>if 
the company is not in the search directory.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Expected completion date: </H3>Expected completion date 
of building work on the new property.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Building work required prior to completion: </H3>What 
building work is remaining before completion of the mortgage can take place. 
Fill in details in the box provided.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Address: </H3>If the company is found in the directory 
search, the address fields of the branch will be automatically populated. If 
not, input the post code and click on the P.A.F search button. Select the 
address required and click on <STRONG>select</STRONG>, this will populate the 
address in the relevant address fields. Click on the <STRONG>Clear 
</STRONG>button to delete all address fields.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Contact details: </H3>Input all details known, once 
completed you can add the address and contact details to the directory by 
clicking on the <STRONG>Add </STRONG>to directory button.
<P></P>
<P>Click <STRONG>OK </STRONG>  when all details completed. </P>
